# UI Rules

## Component Location
- All UI primitives live under `components/ui/`
- Form: `@/components/ui/form` (FormField, FormInput, FormTextArea, FormSwitch, FormCheckbox)
- Combobox: `@/components/ui/combobox/*` (e.g. PortRegionCombobox from `@/components/ui/combobox/port-region-combobox`)
- Confirmation: `@/components/ui/confirmation` (ConfirmationDialog, DeleteConfirmation, etc.)
- Autocomplete: `@/components/ui/autocomplete/*`

## Kendo React UI
- **Inputs**: TextBox, TextArea, Switch, Checkbox from `@progress/kendo-react-inputs`
- **Dropdowns**: ComboBox, DropDownList from `@progress/kendo-react-dropdowns`
- **Buttons**: Button from `@progress/kendo-react-buttons`
- **Dialogs**: Dialog from `@progress/kendo-react-dialog`
- **Grid**: MasterDataGrid (project wrapper); use `serverSidePagination` when needed
- Always use `Controller` from react-hook-form with Kendo components
- Use `fillMode="outline"`, `rounded="medium"` for inputs; `themeColor="primary"` for primary buttons

## Forms
- react-hook-form + zodResolver + zod schema; use Controller with Kendo components

## Form Spacing (Tailwind)
- Form rows / grid: `gap-3` (compact) or `gap-4` (medium)
- Form container: `flex flex-col gap-3`
- Footer: `border-t pt-3`, `flex justify-end gap-2` for actions
- Layout: `grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3`; full-width: `sm:col-span-2`
- FormField label: `mb-1.5`; error: `mt-1`
